Class MMParseTreeListener

  • Object
    • MMBaseListener
      • MMParseTreeListener
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MMIncludeParseTreeListener

    public class MMParseTreeListener
extends MMBaseListener
    A listener that walks the parse tree of a Metamath file and produces effects at specified nodes. Extends the Antlr-provided empty base listener.
